		<text name="info1" extra="true">
			<text>RetroBat is a set of Batch and Powershell scripts written to easily configure and launch EmulationStation for Windows. This frontend software is intended to gather your ROMs collection and run games with compatible emulators such as RetroArch.</text>
		</text>

		<text name="info1" extra="true"  lang="PT">
